title: Tim Daly  / Broken Legs & Toe
description: Dr. Wali helps Sean understand alcohol’s effect on sleep and they both share their love of animals for mental health. Tim Daly tells the cracking tale of breaking his own toe with his bare hands and then breaking both of his legs skiing.
author: info@hazymills.com (Hazy Mills Network)
